ind</span>.<span class=\"name\">CommRing</span>.<span class=\"name\">Mon</span>.<span class=\"name\">divides</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Grind/Ring/CommSolver.html#Lean.Grind.CommRing.Mon\">Mon</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Grind/Ring/CommSolver.html#Lean.Grind.CommRing.Mon\">Mon</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`divides m₁ m₂` returns `true` if monomial `m₁` divides `m₂`\nExample: `x^2.z` divides `w.x^3.y^2.z`\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Arith/Poly.html#Lean.Grind.CommRing.Mon.divides","kind":"def","line":38,"name":"Lean.Grind.CommRing.Mon.divides","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Arith/Poly.lean#L38-L49"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Arith/Poly.html#Lean.Grind.CommRing.Mon.lcm\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">CommRing</span>.<span class=\"name\">Mon</span>.<span class=\"name\">lcm</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Grind/Ring/CommSolver.html#Lean.Grind.CommRing.Mon\">Mon</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Grind/Ring/CommSolver.html#Lean.Grind.CommRing.Mon\">Mon</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Grind/Ring/CommSolver.html#Lean.Grind.CommRing.Mon\">Mon</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`lcm m₁ m₂` returns the least common multiple of the given monomials. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Arith/Poly.html#Lean.Grind.CommRing.Mon.lcm","kind":"def","line":26,"name":"Lean.Grind.CommRing.Mon.lcm","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Arith/Poly.lean#L26-L34"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_na